Innings break What an incredible display from South Africa. They scored 130 from the last 10 overs and 75 from the last five overs. It was all due to Faf du Plessis and David Miller. From 3 for 55, they set new South Africa record for partnerships in ODIs against Australia. Faf made his 10th ODI hundred. David Miller his fifth, and his highest ODI score. Huge task for Australia to chase this down. Join us after the dinner break in 20 minutes time.
